    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast. This vehicle remains in breathtaking, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, free of even the smallest stone chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent, with premium leather upholstery that shows zero signs of wear and a dashboard that remains factory-fresh. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service record from authorized technicians. With exceptionally low mileage and a pedigree of care, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Truly a collector-grade example that must be seen to be appreciated.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
